:{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14299,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/hajj-umrah-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":41184,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Performing Hajj and Umrah together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Subay ibn Ma\u2019bad reported: I raised my voice in preparation for both Umrah and Hajj together. Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou have been guided to the Sunnah\u00a0of your Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1798 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/27\/umar-ibn-al-khattab-inspired\/","url_meta":{"origin":41184,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Umar: If anyone in Ummah is divinely-inspired, it is Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBefore you were nations with divinely inspired people. If such a person were in my nation, it would surely be Umar.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3689 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33190,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/14\/umar-nepotism-betrayal-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":41184,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Nepotism: Betrayal of Islam to favor relatives at expense of others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdul Malik ibn \u2018Umayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever employs a man among his loved ones or relatives, employing him for no other reason besides that, then he has betrayed Allah, His messenger, and the believers.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Fa\u0304ru\u0304q 740 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":41184,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you about the best of this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr and Umar.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 878 Grade\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064f\u062d\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0